%% Diagram: Multi-stage ranking funnel
%% Type: flowchart
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
flowchart LR
    ALL["Inventory<br/>~10,000 candidates"]
    FILTER["Eligibility filter<br/>(blocked, hidden, seen)"]
    LIGHT["Pass 0<br/>Lightweight model<br/>~500 candidates"]
    HEAVY["Pass 1<br/>Multitask NN<br/>~100 candidates"]
    RERANK["Pass 2<br/>Diversity + integrity<br/>~50 posts"]

    ALL --> FILTER --> LIGHT --> HEAVY --> RERANK
